title: USC scores 3 straight TDs, but fall 41-31 to No. 14 Irish
text:
> Indiana USC scores 3 straight TDs, but fall 41-31 to No. 14 Irish Notre Dame's Corey Robinson (88) makes a 10-yard touchdown reception while being defended by Southern California's Iman Marshall (8) during the second half of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in South Bend, Ind. Notre Dame won the game 41-31. (AP Photo/Darron Cummings) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
